  Tan7-si7, chit8-liap8 pio2-a2 kan-ta chit8-kang chun2 chit8-pai2 chong2-si7 be7-iong7--tit. Sou2-i2 goa2 koh khi3 chhoe7 leng7-goa7 chit8-e5 cheng-pio2-sai. I kong2 toa7 lou5-si phaiN2--khi3. Goa2 kong2 ho2-ka-chai3 bo5 sim2-mih8 toa7 cheng3-thau5. Lau2-sit8 kong2, sim2-mih8 si7 toa7 lou5-si goa2 kin-pun2 tioh8 m7-bat. Tan7-si7 goa2 bo5 ai3 ti7 cheng-pio2-sai e5 bin7-thau5-cheng5 kek chit8-khou thui5-thui5. Cheng-pio2-sai chiong toa7 lou5-si siu-li2 ho2-se3. Pio2-a2 chiu7 an2-ni na2-kiaN5 na2-hioh; khi2-mou na7 giang chiu7 ka-ki7 khi2 kiaN5, khi2-mou na7 bai2 chiu7 chu7-tong7 tiaN7--khi3. Mui2-pai2, pio2-a2 teh kiaN5 e5 siaN-im chiu7 chhin-chhiuN7 toa7-hiaN aiN7 sio2-ti7 cho3-hoe2 kiaN5. Goa2 khoaN3 choan5 se3-kai3 chu7-kou2 i2-lai5 bo5 lang5 u7-hoat-tou7 iong7 chit-liap8 pio2-a2 lai5 hun-piat8 chit8-kang e5 si5-kan. Put-tek-i2, goa2 iu7 -koh ka7 pio2-a2 sang3-khi3 siu-li2.
  Chit-pai2 cheng-pio2-sai--e5 kong2 pio2-a2-kiaN3 oan--khi3, toa7-hoat-tiau5 ma7 bo5 chiaN3. I ka7 pio2-a2 siu-li2 liau2 chin ho2-se3. Goa2 e5 pio2-a2 i2-keng oan5-choan5 bo5 bun7-te5. Tan7-si7 keng-koe3 8 tiam2-cheng, pio2-a2 lai7-bin7 teh kiaN5 e5 siaN-im hiong5-hiong5 chhiuN7 phang teh poe e5 siaN-im kang7-khoan2, ji5-chhiaN2 2-ki chiam-a2 tit8-tit8 khai-si2 chhiuN7 teh phang2-se kang7-khoan2, ju2 phang2 ju2 kin2, kin2 kau3 pun be7 chhut tng5-te2-chiam. In khoaN3--khi2-lai5 to7 chhin-chhiuN7 pio2-a2-kiaN3 teng2-bin7 chit8-e5 cheng-bit8 e5 ti-tu-bang7. Soa3--loh8-khi3, pio2-a2 ti7 lak8, chhit hun lai7 to7 kiaN5 oan5 24 tiam2-cheng, jian5-au7 hoat-chhut chit8-siaN to7 iu7-koh tiann7--khi3. Goa2 khi2-mou chiok-bai2, koh ka7 pio2-a2 sang3 khi3 chhoe7 leng7-goa7 chit8-e5 cheng-pio2-sai. Cheng-pio2 sai--e5 khoaN3 liau2, ka7 pio2-a2 pak--khui. In-ui7 chit-e5 bun7-te5 i2-keng chin giam5-tiong7, sou2-i2 goa2 chun2-pi7 beh ka7 cheng-pio2 sai--e5 mng7 hou7 chheng-chho2. Chit-liap8 pio2-a2 si7 goa2 khai 200 khou be2--e5, tan7-si7 siu-li2 e5 chiN5 na2-chhiuN7 i2-keng khai 2, 3 chheng khou--lah. 
  Tng goa2 teh tan2 i siu-li2 pio2-a2 e5-si5, goa2 chiah hoat-kak chit-e5 cheng-pio2 sai--e5 si7 goa2 sek8-sai7 e5 lang5. I si7 chun5-a2-teng2 e5 chit8-e5 kang-teng5-su, m7-ku2 m7-si7 chit8-e5 chin gau5 e5 kang-teng5-su. I ka7 pio2-a2 khoaN3 liau2, chiu7 chhin-chhiuN7 ki5-tha e5 cheng-pio2-sai kang7-khoan2, iong7 chu7-sin3 boan2-boan2 e5 khau2-khi3 kong2,“Li2 pio2-a2 lai7-bin7 e5 chui2-khi3 siuN che7......”Goa2 tong-tiuN5 chiu7 ka7 pio2-a2 kong3--phoa3, bo5 ai3 koh siu-li2--lah. 
  Goa2 e5 A-ku7 William (i2-keng koe3-sin--khi3-ah) tiaN7-tiaN7 kong2, ” Chit8 chiah ho2 be2 na7 bat thau-chau2--koe3, chiu7 i2-keng m7-si7 ho2-be2; chit8-liap8 ho2 pio2-a2 na7 bat siu-li2--koe3, chiu7 m7-si7 ho2 pio2-a2.” Goa2 chit-ma2 ju2 siuN7 ju2 u7 to7-li2. 
  (Tai5-oan5-ji7 Chap8-chi3 te7 5 ki5, 2001 ni5 1 geh8) 
